OL,3,CFreedom of Information requests
OL,4,Ccosting Jersey's government #1m a year
OL,6,FJersey's Deputy Chief Minister has
OL,7,Frevealed it's costing the Government
OL,8,Faround #1m a year to deal with Freedom
OL,9,Fof Information requests.
OL,11,FWhen the FOI law came into force in
OL,12,FJersey, officials anticipated
OL,13,Freceiving around 60 requests each
OL,14,Fyear, but there are now around 1,000
OL,15,Fannually.
