OL,3,CFreedom of Information requests
OL,4,Ccosting Jersey's government #1m a year
OL,6,F"It's my own view that we don't really
OL,7,Fhave enough trust in Government so
OL,8,Fwhat we're trying to do is improve
OL,9,Fpeople's trust so they ask fewer
OL,10,Fquestions."
OL,12,FIt's now more than 10 years since
OL,13,FStates Members voted to extend the
OL,14,Fscope of the FOI law to cover arms-
OL,15,Flength organisations, a change that
OL,16,Fwould allow the public to request
OL,17,Finformation about their work and
OL,18,Ffinances.
