OL,3,CFreedom of Information requests
OL,4,Ccosting Jersey's government #1m a year
OL,6,FJohn Baker, of the Jersey Action
OL,7,FGroup, said: "It was promised by the
OL,8,Fgovernment and (then-Chief Minister)
OL,9,FDeputy Ian Gorst, but nobody has done
OL,10,Fanything about it.
OL,12,F"What's the matter with them? There
OL,13,Fare quangos going out there, doing
OL,14,Fwhat they like."
